I am eager to join GIKnowledge Building 2025 because it offers a rare opportunity to gain hands-on learning experience from leading professionals through interactive classes and mentorship. As a student who has worked as a research assistant for over a year, I believe this program will help me bridge the gap between academic knowledge and real-world applications in industry and technology.  Participating in GIKnowledge Building will allow me to better understand how strategic thinking, innovation, and cross-sector collaboration shape impactful solutions to todays challenges. I also hope to refine my analytical and research skills in a dynamic and multidisciplinary setting, something that aligns closely with both my academic background and personal aspirations.
